@page "/Receiving"
@model Abs.FixedAssets.Pages.Receiving.ControlCenterModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Receiving Control Center";
    ViewData["TabTitle"] = "Receiving";
    Layout = "_ModernLayout";
}

@*
    Sprint 11 PR #5 — first live Control Center surface.

    The four-quadrant scaffold (KPI strip + exception lane + drawer + activity feed)
    is rendered by _ControlCenterShell. All data comes from
    IReceivingControlCenterService (PR #3); the voice-tool surface (PR #4) is
    wired through the Voice FAB inside the shell.

    Route note: this lives at /Receiving/ControlCenter for the duration of
    Sprint 11. PR #7 (kill list) will swap /Receiving → this page and redirect
    the old Cockpit to /Receiving/Cockpit-Legacy. Doing the swap then keeps
    the destructive change at the end of the sprint, when every Control Center
    primitive + service + voice tool has shipped and shipped clean.
*@

@await Html.PartialAsync("_ControlCenterShell", Model.Shell)
